\": 430, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"800m\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"heats\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"17-year-oldBritishdebutantPhoebe\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"inParis\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tokyo 2020 and two-time world silver medallist Hodgkinson, who two weeks ago lowered the British record to a world-leading 1:54.61 at the Diamond League meet in London, was the fastest finisher in the fourth of six heats at Stade De France, crossing the line in 1:59.31.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9062088143017994, \"rank\": 0.1034984257592003, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999887302554484, \"rank\": 1.1269871570300576e-05, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9999999495676105, \"rank\": 5.04323770623359e-08, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}, {\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.214282979439621e-21, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999997718250857, \"rank\": 2.2816849079970476e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a world-leading 1:54.61\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest finisher\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth of six heats\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"Stade De France\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"1:59.31\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gill clawed her way back after dropping to fourth to secure the last of three berths available from her heat in 1:58.83, while Tokyo fourth-place finisherJemma Reekiegot the job done with a first-place finish from the opening group in 2:00.00.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"her way\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"three berths\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"her heat\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"1:58.83\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"a first-place finish\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening group\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"2:00.00\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson said: \\\"I do not really like heats.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1065, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999887302554484, \"rank\": 1.1269871570300576e-05, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heats\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are not my favourite.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was just glad to qualify.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought the girls really stepped up, because I was looking at their heats and I was like, 'that's quite tough, actually, for a heat.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"their heats\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"a heat\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[Heats] are worse than the final, to be honest.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Heats\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final you know you are just giving everything and that's that.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the heats and the rounds you have to contend with people giving it their absolute all, you are trying to conserve energy, at the same time you do not want to make a mistake.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"the rounds\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"their absolute all\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I am definitely glad that's done.\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just glad to make it through safely.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The semis will be fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The semis\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson, ranked world number one at her signature distance, stormed to a surprise silver three summers ago, breaking Dame Kelly Holmes' 26-year-old British record in the process.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999887302554484, \"rank\": 1.1269871570300576e-05, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1823, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dame Kelly Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\"}, {\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9999999495676105, \"rank\": 5.04323770623359e-08, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world number\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1