rce/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9555778293611933, \"rank\": 0.04648037003430785, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday evening\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like things can happen at championships, I feel like Phoebe has done really well.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2278, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Buffay\", \"score\": 0.9999995537124137, \"rank\": 4.462876431726134e-07, \"text\": \"Phoebe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Buffay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Buffay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"championships\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's taking it all in her stride.\\\"\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her stride\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Hodgkinson elected to run the 400m at June's British championships it was St Albans' teenager Gill who beat Reekie to the national title and booked herself a spot on Team GB.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999887302554484, \"rank\": 1.1269871570300576e-05, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2394, \"end\": 2415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999983247108, \"rank\": 1.6753495321070983e-09, \"text\": \"British championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 2423, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/St_Albans\", \"score\": 0.9999999992687663, \"rank\": 7.29740973515559e-10, \"text\": \"St Albans\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/St_Albans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/St_Albans\"}, {\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3409179300667718e-13, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"Reekie\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"the national title\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was as recently as June 2023 that Gill won the 800m title at the English Schools championship, and by May had lowered her personal best to 1:57:86 at the Irish Milers meeting in Belfast, a time the Deborah Steer-coached athlete said made her feel instantly \\\"older\\\".\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2682, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9113746408839419, \"rank\": 0.0823804245467882, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2706, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"score\": 0.9999999986430339, \"rank\": 1.3536961643695587e-09, \"text\": \"Belfast\", \"types\": 