am\": \"that schools title\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"14 teenagers\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"It's very emotional being out there.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's my first time in that sort of arena, and, you know, it's the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first time\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"that sort\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3082}, {\"ngram\": \"arena\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the best competition in athletics, and seeing my face on the screen when the camera came around, I was trying not to cry.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best competition\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3152}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"the screen\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was like, you can not break down before doing 800 metres!\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"800 metres\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Even) in that cool room, and having that camera on me, it's something new to me.\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that cool room\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"that camera\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it really reminds me, I am in a top league now.\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a top league\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud of myself, because I was looking at photos of myself yesterday, doing primary school cross-country league, and I just think she would be so happy that I am here now in Paris, doing the Olympics, because it was a big dream of mine.\\\"\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3634, \"end\": 3639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4953211046483503e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"primary school cross-country league\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3571}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"a big dream\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3687}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Friday was the first time the Paris track had been tested and by all appearances it seems to be a fast one, with 15 women breaking two minutes in the 800m heats.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3729, \"end\": 3734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4953211046483503e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"all appearances\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"a fast one\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"15 women\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3820}, {\"ngram\": \"two minutes\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m heats\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeing my face on the screen when the camera came arou